Decisions
---------
- e/r/u compose onto the current filter; a resets to a zero model.Filter{}.
- setReadCmd returns readToggledMsg (confirm-by-id); under an unread-only filter
  the handler re-queries so a now-read item drops out, otherwise confirms in
  place.
- markAllReadCmd returns reloadMsg rather than tea.Sequence, guaranteeing the
  re-query runs after the write.
- Source scoping (SourceIDs) deferred (store supports it; no key/UI this step).
- Filter/read wiring only; background sync engine (R force-sync), Gmail provider,
  and open-in-browser remain deferred (steps 06/07).
